description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, an iconic episode with layers, a hypnotist, and Mary at home. After the recap, Danny chats with Dr. Tiffany Moon from The Real Housewives of Dallas about her first season, current relationship with the other women, and more.


Dr. Tiffany Moon Interview: 28:35ish
